{
  "stem": "10572.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had two friends, one of them a very close friend of mine, who later on stayed a very close friend of mine when he was-- became a great rabbi in Olympia Fields, Frank Rosenthal.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was-- had volunteered for the wash kitchen, to-- together with another rabbi, Egon [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Loewenstein, ?] to be able to say Kaddish for those who died.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I came in, they belonged to our group, to our youth group.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I came in and he saw me, the kapo came with two other kapos.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he asked me, in front of the other kapos again, what did I say?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father always taught me that if you say A, you also have to say B.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And therefore, I repeated what I-- I knew I was going anyhow, so I wanted at least-- die with dignity.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had gone-- before, before I went to the wash kitchen, I went to Baracke 1A, the barrack I stayed in, to tell my brother-in-law and-- what had happened to me so that they knew where I was-- where they finished me off.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I went there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I repeated and told them what I'd said, they put me over a block and gave me the usual punishment of 25 slashes with a two-by-four over my back and broke vertebra, broke discs that I have lived with the rest of my life.",
      "word_count": 46
    }
  ],
